OL,4,CCovid: Live events to be protected by
OL,5,C#750m government insurance scheme
OL,6, UK music festivals and other live
OL,7, events are to be protected by a
OL,8, government-backed insurance scheme if
OL,9, they have to cancel because of Covid.
OL,11,FIt will begin next month with a #750m
OL,12,Fbudget to cover cancellation costs if
OL,13,Fevents are legally unable to happen due
OL,14,Fto government Covid restrictions.
OL,16,FThe live events industry, which has
OL,17,Frepeatedly called for such a plan,
OL,18,Fbroadly welcomed the announcement.
OL,20,FMore than half of all music festivals
OL,21,Fhave been cancelled this summer.
